<div type="definition">
<p>SHORT SENTENCE OFTEN USED USED by ALL FOR EXPRESSING an ACCEPTED TRUTH OR COMMON OPINION.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general specific term for a proverb or common saying is yán 諺.</p>
<p>2. Yǔ 語 regularly refers to popular current sayings.</p>
<p>3. Yán 言 refers to bon-mots, proverbs and sayings of any kind, including attributed maxims by philosophers and the like.</p>
        </div>
